<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MedPulse - Decoding MBBS Education</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN for styling -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <!-- FontAwesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans tracking-wide">

    <!-- Header / Navigation -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#" class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-stethoscopes"></i>
                <span>MedPulse</span>
            </a>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 font-medium">
                <a href="#home" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Home</a>
                <a href="#journey" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">The Journey</a>
                <a href="#difficulty" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Why It's Hard</a>
                <a href="#cost" class="hover:text-red-600 transition">Why It's Costly</a>
            </nav>
            <a href="#journey" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-red-700 transition hidden md:inline-block">Explore Guide</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="home" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-indigo-50 py-20 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl text-center">
            <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 text-xs uppercase font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">The Reality of Medical Education</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mt-4 leading-tight">
                Demystifying the <span class="text-red-600">MBBS Journey</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg md:text-xl mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                An honest, data-driven look at what it truly takes to become a doctor—exploring the immense academic pressure, lifestyle shifts, and financial realities.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="#difficulty" class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition">Understand the Rigor</a>
                <a href="#cost" class="bg-white text-gray-900 border border-gray-300 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 transition">Analyze Costs</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Student Journey Overview -->
    <section id="journey" class="py-20 px-6 container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">The 5-Year Roadmap</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">A standard breakdown of how a medical student evolves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 font-bold text-xl mb-6">1</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Foundations (Years 1-2)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Diving straight into heavy theory: Anatomy, Physiology, and Biochemistry. Students transition from general science to rigorous memorization.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 font-bold text-xl mb-6">2</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Para-Clinical Phase (Year 3)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Understanding diseases, drugs, and forensics through Pathology, Microbiology, and Pharmacology. This bridges theory with hospital applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 font-bold text-xl mb-6">3</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Clinical Rotations (Years 4-5)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">The ultimate challenge. Students work directly in hospital wards across Surgery, Medicine, and Pediatrics, balancing real patient care with final board exams.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why MBBS is Difficult -->
    <section id="difficulty" class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-20 px-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">Academic & Mental Strain</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-2">Why is MBBS Considered So Difficult?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl mt-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-medical"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">The Volume of Content</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">It is often compared to "drinking water from a firehose." The sheer volume of facts, drug interactions, anomalies, and surgical terms required for safe medical practice is unmatched by any other undergraduate degree.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl mt-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Zero Margin for Error</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Unlike fields where errors mean bad code or miscalculated balances, errors in medicine mean jeopardized human lives. This psychological realization adds massive daily anxiety for students during clinical postings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl mt-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Sleep Deprivation & Shift Work</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Balancing 8 hours of morning lectures and afternoon clinics with sudden 12-hour or 24-hour night calls during rotations creates extreme physical exhaustion that impacts personal lives.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <div class="text-red-500 text-2xl mt-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">The Never-Ending Exam Cycle</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Education doesn't stop at MBBS. To practice successfully, students must immediately prepare for grueling licensing exams and competitive post-graduate residency matches.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why MBBS is Expensive -->
    <section id="cost" class="py-20 px-6 container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">Financial Economics</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2">Why is Private Medical School So Expensive?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto mt-3">Private medical tuition can look shocking. Here is the actual infrastructure and operational cost breakdown behind those premium fees.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-center">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-hospital"></i>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Hospital Maintenance</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Medical colleges must fully run or heavily subsidize dynamic, tertiary teaching hospitals to guarantee students exposure to actual patients.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-center">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-microscope"></i>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">High-Tech Labs & Simulators</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dissection halls, high-fidelity robotic patient mannequins, biochemistry analyzers, and modern pathology labs require massive capital to build and safely run.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-center">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-doctor"></i>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Specialist Faculty Ratios</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Medical regulatory councils enforce strict student-to-professor ratios. Hiring actively practicing, specialized doctors to teach requires highly competitive salaries.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 py-12 px-6 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-xl font-bold text-white">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-stethoscopes text-red-500"></i>
                <span>MedPulse</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-center md:text-left">&copy; 2026 MedPulse Educational Platform. Built for medical transparency.</p>
            <div class="flex space-x-6 text-lg">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
